msgctxt "an5.153:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.153:0.2"
msgid "16. Saddhammavagga "
msgstr "16. The True Teaching "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.153:0.3"
msgid "153. Tatiyasammattaniyāmasutta "
msgstr "153. Inevitability Regarding the Right Path (3rd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.176, sc1
msgctxt "an5.153:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato suṇantopi saddhammaṃ abhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, someone with five qualities is unable to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities even when listening to the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an5.153:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. VAR: upārambhacitto → saupārambhacitto (s1-3, km)
#. VAR: khīlajāto → khilajāto (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.153:1.3"
msgid "Makkhī dhammaṃ suṇāti makkhapariyuṭṭhito, upārambhacitto dhammaṃ suṇāti randhagavesī, dhammadesake āhatacitto hoti khīlajāto, duppañño hoti jaḷo eḷamūgo, anaññāte aññātamānī hoti. "
msgstr "They listen to the teaching bent only on putting it down. They listen to the teaching with a hostile, fault-finding mind. They’re antagonistic to the teacher, planning to attack them. They’re witless, dull, and stupid. And they think they know what they don’t know. "

msgctxt "an5.153:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato suṇantopi saddhammaṃ abhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ. "
msgstr "Someone with these five qualities is unable to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities even when listening to the true teaching. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.153:2.1"
msgid "Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato suṇanto saddhammaṃ bhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattaṃ. "
msgstr "Someone with five qualities is able to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities when listening to the true teaching. "

msgctxt "an5.153:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.153:2.3"
msgid "Amakkhī dhammaṃ suṇāti na makkhapariyuṭṭhito, anupārambhacitto dhammaṃ suṇāti na randhagavesī, dhammadesake anāhatacitto hoti akhīlajāto, paññavā hoti ajaḷo aneḷamūgo, na anaññāte aññātamānī hoti. "
msgstr "They don’t listen to the teaching bent only on putting it down. They don’t listen to the teaching with a hostile, fault-finding mind. They’re not antagonistic to the teacher, and not planning to attack them. They’re wise, bright, and clever. And they don’t think they know what they don’t know. "

msgctxt "an5.153:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato suṇanto saddhammaṃ bhabbo niyāmaṃ okkamituṃ kusalesu dhammesu sammattan”ti. "
msgstr "Someone with these five qualities is able to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities when listening to the true teaching.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.153:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

